<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFStevenson_and_Ho">Stevenson and Ho, Barbara and Cynthia O (New York). <i>Crossing the Bridge&#160;: Comparative Essays on Medieval European and Heian Japanese Women Writers</i>. 2000: Palgrave.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Crossing+the+Bridge+%3A+Comparative+Essays+on+Medieval+European+and+Heian+Japanese+Women+Writers&amp;rft.aulast=Stevenson+and+Ho&amp;rft.aufirst=Barbara+and+Cynthia+O&amp;rft.au=Stevenson+and+Ho%2C+Barbara+and+Cynthia+O&amp;rft.date=New+York&amp;rft.place=2000&amp;rft.pub=Palgrave&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:The_Tale_of_Genji"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFTyler1999">Tyler, Royall (1999). ""I Am I": Genji and Murasaki". <i>Monumenta Nipponica</i> <b>54(4)</b>: 435–480.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=%22I+Am+I%22%3A+Genji+and+Murasaki&amp;rft.jtitle=Monumenta+Nipponica&amp;rft.aulast=Tyler&amp;rft.aufirst=Royall&amp;rft.au=Tyler%2C+Royall&amp;rft.date=1999&amp;rft.volume=54%284%29&amp;rft.pages=435%E2%80%93480&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:The_Tale_of_Genji"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFTyler2001">Tyler, Royall (2001). <i>The Tale of Genji</i>. New York: Viking.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Tale+of+Genji&amp;rft.aulast=Tyler&amp;rft.aufirst=Royall&amp;rft.au=Tyler%2C+Royall&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=Viking&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:The_Tale_of_Genji"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFTyler2002">Tyler, Royall (March 2002). "<a href="http://wwwsshe.murdoch.edu.au/intersections/issue7/tyler.html" class="external text" title="http://wwwsshe.murdoch.edu.au/intersections/issue7/tyler.html" rel="nofollow">Marriage, Rank and Rape in <i>The Tale of Genji</i></a>". <i>Intersections: Gender, History and Culture in the Asian Context</i> <b>7</b><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://wwwsshe.murdoch.edu.au/intersections/issue7/tyler.html" class="external free" title="http://wwwsshe.murdoch.edu.au/intersections/issue7/tyler.html" rel="nofollow">http://wwwsshe.murdoch.edu.au/intersections/issue7/tyler.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Marriage%2C+Rank+and+Rape+in+%27%27The+Tale+of+Genji%27%27&amp;rft.jtitle=Intersections%3A+Gender%2C+History+and+Culture+in+the+Asian+Context&amp;rft.aulast=Tyler&amp;rft.aufirst=Royall&amp;rft.au=Tyler%2C+Royall&amp;rft.date=March+2002&amp;rft.volume=7&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwwwsshe.murdoch.edu.au%2Fintersections%2Fissue7%2Ftyler.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:The_Tale_of_Genji"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFTyler2002">Tyler, Royall and Susan (2002). "The Possession of Ukifune". <i>Asiatica Venetiana</i> <b>5</b>: 177–209.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+Possession+of+Ukifune&amp;rft.jtitle=Asiatica+Venetiana&amp;rft.aulast=Tyler&amp;rft.aufirst=Royall+and+Susan&amp;rft.au=Tyler%2C+Royall+and+Susan&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.volume=5&amp;rft.pages=177%E2%80%93209&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:The_Tale_of_Genji"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFTyler2003">Tyler, Royall (2003). "Rivalry, Triumph, Folly, Revenge: A Plot Line through the <i>Tale of Genji</i>". <i>Journal of Japanese Studies</i> <b>29(2)</b>: 251–87.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Rivalry%2C+Triumph%2C+Folly%2C+Revenge%3A+A+Plot+Line+through+the+%27%27Tale+of+Genji%27%27&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+Japanese+Studies&amp;rft.aulast=Tyler&amp;rft.aufirst=Royall&amp;rft.au=Tyler%2C+Royall&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.volume=29%282%29&amp;rft.pages=251%E2%80%9387&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:The_Tale_of_Genji"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFUry1988">Ury, Marian (1988). "A Heian Note on the Supernatural". <i>The Journal of the Association of Teachers of Japanese</i> <b>22(2)</b>: 189–94.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=A+Heian+Note+on+the+Supernatural&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Journal+of+the+Association+of+Teachers+of+Japanese&amp;rft.aulast=Ury&amp;rft.aufirst=Marian&amp;rft.au=Ury%2C+Marian&amp;rft.date=1988&amp;rft.volume=22%282%29&amp;rft.pages=189%E2%80%9394&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:The_Tale_of_Genji"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFLwarence1958">Lwarence, Hollendaisde (1958) (in Japanese). <i>Nihon Koten Bungaku Taikei 14: Genji Monogatari 1</i>. <a href="/wiki/Tokyo" title="Tokyo">Tōkyō</a>: <a href="/wiki/Iwanami_Shoten_Publishing" title="Iwanami Shoten Publishing">Iwanami Shoten</a>. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/4000600141" class="internal">ISBN 4-000-60014-1</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Nihon+Koten+Bungaku+Taikei+14%3A+Genji+Monogatari+1&amp;rft.aulast=Lwarence&amp;rft.aufirst=Hollendaisde&amp;rft.au=Lwarence%2C+Hollendaisde&amp;rft.date=1958&amp;rft.place=%5B%5BTokyo%7CT%C5%8Dky%C5%8D%5D%5D&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BIwanami+Shoten+Publishing%7CIwanami+Shoten%5D%5D&amp;rft.isbn=4-000-60014-1&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:The_Tale_of_Genji"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
